# Tidewater environment variables — template.
#
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) for local overrides. Phase 1 needs none: the CDK
# app runs region-agnostic, the dashboard has no runtime config yet, and secrets
# (the dashboard bearer token) live in SSM Parameter Store, never here — see
# docs/architecture.md §7 and CLAUDE.md ("Secrets ... never env vars").
#
# Variables will be added in later phases (e.g. CDK_DEFAULT_ACCOUNT /
# CDK_DEFAULT_REGION for deploys in Phase 2). Document each one here as it lands.
